    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你喘着粗气醒来，咳出PFC液体时肺部灼痛。在迷失与孤独中，你发现自己被困在一座废弃的空间站里。但你并非真正的孤独——异常现象已吞噬了这里！你唯一的生存机会是抵达<strong><i>8号机库</i></strong>，在这场循环噩梦为时已晚前逃脱！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204650/extras/07b5caa652c442ad3e7c06b06578c92d.poster.avif?t=1747820531\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204650/extras/07b5caa652c442ad3e7c06b06578c92d.webm?t=1747820531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204650/extras/07b5caa652c442ad3e7c06b06578c92d.mp4?t=1747820531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>8号机库</strong></i>是什么？你要做什么？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>8号机库</i></strong>是一款受<i>出口8</i>启发的科幻步行模拟器与恐怖找茬游戏的结合体。在以第0层为参考的同时，警惕第1至8层中的异常。异常可能是环境中不对劲的事物，也可能是致命怪物或超自然实体。发现异常就回头——否则只需继续前进！<strong><i>8号机库</i></strong>旨在营造紧张的心理恐怖氛围，让你在收集关键物品和阅读失踪船员日志以逃脱循环噩梦的过程中质疑自己的理智！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204650/extras/c10c212b89fc5f41a964a5e8e6defe33.poster.avif?t=1747820531\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204650/extras/c10c212b89fc5f41a964a5e8e6defe33.webm?t=1747820531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204650/extras/c10c212b89fc5f41a964a5e8e6defe33.mp4?t=1747820531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>8号机库</strong></i>有什么内容？</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>完整的科幻心理恐怖体验！</strong> <i>8号机库</i>是开发者倾注热情独立完成的游戏，包含明确的开端、发展和单一结局。结局虽唯一，但随着你发现所有异常，每次游玩都会有细微差异。未来所有更新免费！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>58种异常待发现！</strong> 为多次逃脱尝试提供重玩价值。已发现的异常在全部50种被找到前不会重复。<i>(开启额外模式可激活全部异常迎接更高挑战！)</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集6个逃脱必备关键物品！</strong> 同时寻找空间站中隐藏的6本可选日志以了解游戏背景！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204650/extras/72440448e2d80e37bf40ebe81450f68a.poster.avif?t=1747820531\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204650/extras/72440448e2d80e37bf40ebe81450f68a.webm?t=1747820531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204650/extras/72440448e2d80e37bf40ebe81450f68a.mp4?t=1747820531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>交互式物体！</strong> 让你沉浸于恐怖的找茬解谜中。探索环境以找到逃离被诅咒空间站的方法！你需要检查板条箱内部，甚至打开淋浴器来确认楼层无异常。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>单次游玩30至120分钟以上！</strong> 时长取决于你的观察力和异常随机算法的运气。<i>(自动保存功能助你随时暂停！)</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8项成就待解锁！</strong> 其中一项将考验你的速通技巧！<i>8号机库</i>内置计时器并与Speedrun.com官方排行榜联动，供挑战开发者（就是我！）和优化逃脱时间的玩家使用！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204650/extras/2f9f4ab6a5f23c68717a3a9e2806752d.poster.avif?t=1747820531\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204650/extras/2f9f4ab6a5f23c68717a3a9e2806752d.webm?t=1747820531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204650/extras/2f9f4ab6a5f23c68717a3a9e2806752d.mp4?t=1747820531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独立开发者的处女作 :3</p>",
